#define MemSize 25 //    
class TStack
{
 protected:
    int Mem[MemSize]; //   
    int Top; //    
 public:
    TStack () { Top = -1; }
    int IsEmpty (void) const { Top == -1; }
    int IsFull (void) const { Top == MemSize-1;}
    void Put ( const int Val ) { Mem[++Top] = val; }
    TData Get (void) { return Mem[Top--]; }
};
